      "text": "……",
      "docImage": "counseling_sheet",
      "docNeedConfirm": true
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "（ふふ…処女か……。色々と楽しめそうだな。）",
      "conditions": {
        "route": "virgin"
      }
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "（なんだ、処女じゃないのか……。経験があるなら多少激しくやっても問題なさそうだな。）",
      "conditions": {
        "route": "experienced"
      }
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "ありがとう。……ふむ、なるほどね。"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "じゃあね、念のためなんだけど、こっちの「施術同意書」にもサインだけお願いできるかな？"
